Thumb marks in amphora called Dressel 20 (Palma del Río, Seville) <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-27916" src="http://www.dayofarchaeology.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/sei.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1483" />

